text: Md. Iqbal (1948–18 January 2005) is a Jatiya Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Pabna-5. ==Career== Iqbal was elected to parliament from Pabna-5 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party (Ershad) politicians Category:1948 births Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:2005 deaths
